::Prowl::

Prowl turned, looking at Symphony as the bot approached. He walked 
forward, stopping several feet away from the bot.

"Yup, I'm a Maximal," he says, stretching out a hand for Symphony to 
shake. "My name is Prowl. Nice to meet you. I'll let you know if you 
can join as soon as I get our leader's authorization."

-Love,- he thinks over his psychic link with Iron Raptor, -Is it 
allright for this bot to join?-
